oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Holy Cross Catholic Church altar
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of the altar at Holy Cross Catholic Church on South Wood Street. A thurible is hanging from the ceiling in front of the altar. Statues of the Virgin Mary and Jesus Christ are positioned on either side.
